content: Jesus Predicts the Destruction of the Temple(A)
Then as He went out of the temple, one of His disciples said to Him, “Teacher, see what manner of stones and what buildings ”
And Jesus answered and said to him,
The Signs of the Times and the End of the Age(D)
Now as He sat on the Mount of Olives opposite the temple, Peter, James, John, and Andrew asked Him privately,
“Tell us, when will these things be? And what  the sign when all these things will be fulfilled?”
And Jesus, answering them, began to say:
